  "extract": "The Japan national football team , also known by the nickname Samurai Blue , represents Japan in men's international football. It is controlled by the Japan Football Association (JFA), the governing body for football in Japan.",
  "extract_html": "<p>The <b>Japan national football team</b><span style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </span>, also known by the nickname <b>Samurai Blue</b><span style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </span>, represents Japan in men's international football. It is controlled by the Japan Football Association (JFA), the governing body for football in Japan.</p>"
